{"tid":1208371,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"我個仔問我：「做咩要bang佢既？」","createTime":"2019-06-12T09:23:02.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-13T01:01:17.000Z","uid":31884,"like":161,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"4222a075236d3419f44d9a39fb007b5bfada9c2f","tid":1208371,"uid":31884,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:23:02.000Z","msg":"岩岩接完個仔放學返到屋企，佢今年3歲讀緊N班，一返到屋企見到媽咪睇緊有線直播。<br />\n<br />\n黑色防暴衫既呀蛇拎住支pain ball咁既槍bang bang bang，然後又有另一個呀蛇放催淚彈。<br />\n<br />\n我個仔問我：「做咩要bang佢既？佢bang緊邊個呀？」<br />\n<br />\n我下意識想講警察叔叔bang壞人，但我無即刻講出口，我諗咗半粒鍾都唔識解釋。<br />\n<br />\n有無人話我知點答我個仔，佢好專心睇緊警察叔叔bang bang bang....<br />\n<br />\n一bang又問，一bang又問....<br />\n<br />\n爸爸出去保護香港啦，你今晚同媽咪覺豬，唔好扭計啦，別了，吾愛。"},{"pid":"bad897b68e58f60526383ad102fdcf3ff5130ad4","tid":1208371,"uid":149844,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:25:49.000Z","msg":"各位打工仔同爸爸 <br />\n你地仲有良知就快啲出嚟幫手<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n已有2位市民中槍"},{"pid":"65e223f6b91ab1845326dbd70ffe9c63460d2498","tid":1208371,"uid":85980,"like":18,"dislike":0,"score":18,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:26:34.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZVsFUK9.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZVsFUK9.jpg&h=fdbc555a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"3ef6beb5f454a95952f0620a17ba8d8ae5f339df","tid":1208371,"uid":23707,"like":11,"dislike":0,"score":11,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-12T09:28:32.000Z","msg":"睇到呢個post好想喊<br />\n我都唔知應該點同我個仔解釋 同你個仔差唔多大<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"25034568713bb6436fe8544dd6138b06ebba02a4","tid":1208371,"uid":31884,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"3ef6beb5f454a95952f0620a17ba8d8ae5f339df","tid":1208371,"uid":23707,"like":11,"dislike":0,"scor